00:10:16,688 --> 00:10:18,983
fun zayn, shvester.

199
00:10:18,983 --> 00:10:21,984
nu, itster iz er shoyn nito, lang geshtorbn.

200
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:25,646
 lebn im shteyt a tsveyter bruder mayn foter's.

201
00:10:25,703 --> 00:10:27,435
 der, dos iz Berl.

202
00:10:27,694 --> 00:10:30,219
, im hot men aroysgefirt in Sibir

203
00:10:30,428 --> 00:10:33,411
mit di mishpokhe, mit di froy un mit tsvey kleyne kinder,

204
00:10:33,411 --> 00:10:35,304
vayle zey hobn ⟨gehat⟩ a kleyne kremele.

205
00:10:35,304 --> 00:10:38,459
⟨nu⟩, zaynen geven burzhuyen, heyst es, far, damolst hot ⟨es⟩ azoy geheysn.

206
00:10:38,528 --> 00:10:39,807
nor, ⟨⟩,

207
00:10:40,182 --> 00:10:41,543
paradoksal,

208
00:10:41,582 --> 00:10:43,904
nor a dank dem zaynen zey geblibn lebn,

209
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:47,094
un, nokh dem vi Stalin iz geshtorbn,

210
00:10:47,269 --> 00:10:51,265
in, f-, zibn un fuftsik, akht un fuftsik, zaynen zey gekumen tsurik

211
00:10:51,265 --> 00:10:53,473
in Lite, un gelebt in Vilne.

212
00:10:53,766 --> 00:10:57,188
 itster, er iz geshtorbn ⟨zayn-⟩ un di tante iz geshtorbn.

213
00:10:57,188 --> 00:11:00,425
der zun zeyerer lebt in, Erets-Yisroel.

214
00:11:00,702 --> 00:11:04,006
 do in briln shteyt, un halt di hant oyf mayn,

215
00:11:04,006 --> 00:11:06,216
 mame's, VOT, pleytse,

216
00:11:06,216 --> 00:11:07,833
dos iz, onkl Mikhl,

217
00:11:08,008 --> 00:11:11,377
 mayn foter's, bruder, yingster bruder,

218
00:11:11,518 --> 00:11:14,684
velkher hot gelebt in Pariz, geven a advokat,

219
00:11:14,775 --> 00:11:16,541
un iz heldish umgekumen.

220
00:11:16,952 --> 00:11:20,557
me hot im dershosn, di daytshn, dershosn als a eruvnik.

221
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:25,538
un, di daytshn hobn damolst imitirt, az dos iz nit poshet me shist yidn,

222
00:11:25,538 --> 00:11:28,939
nor az dos iz, bashtroft far umruikeyt vos s'iz geven,

223
00:11:28,939 --> 00:11:30,548
 in Frankraykh.

224
00:11:30,587 --> 00:11:33,011
hot men dershosn damolst draytsn mentshn.

225
00:11:33,102 --> 00:11:35,587
es iz do, in shtub hob ikh dos,

226
00:11:35,587 --> 00:11:37,702
 es iz do der,

227
00:11:38,164 --> 00:11:40,532
 di meldung vegn dem, vi m'hot zey dershosn.

228
00:11:40,532 --> 00:11:45,937
emes, vegn, ⟨, l- v-⟩ lebn zayn familye iz ongeshribn "JUIF," dos heyst yi- a yid.

229
00:11:46,382 --> 00:11:49,720
 di, LOUIS ARAGON hot in zayn tsayt bashribn

230
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,492
vi heldish er iz geshtorbn.

231
00:11:51,492 --> 00:11:55,795
di daytsh, der daytsh vos hot ge-, ge- ge- oysgefilt di ekzekutsye

232
00:11:55,795 --> 00:11:58,863
hot im, forgeleygt az me zol im farbindn di oygn,

233
00:11:59,123 --> 00:12:02,351
nor er hot zikh antzagt, un az er iz shoyn geven a toyter,

234
00:12:02,351 --> 00:12:03,988
hot der STÜLPNAGEL,

235
00:12:03,988 --> 00:12:05,566
velkher hot ge- ge-

236
00:12:05,566 --> 00:12:07,945
ge- mit di ekzekutsye ongefirt,

237
00:12:07,945 --> 00:12:11,664
hot er azoy a brik geton un gezogt, "JA, DAS WAR EIN MANN."

238
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:14,743
 ⟨nu, ot⟩ shteyt mayn mame,

239
00:12:15,829 --> 00:12:17,308
Taybe, Taybele.

240
00:12:20,132 --> 00:12:21,358
⟨⟩, dos bin ikh,

241
00:12:22,393 --> 00:12:25,272
⟨⟩, vi ir zet, mit, in, in a shul-forme.

242
00:12:26,798 --> 00:12:28,381
 mir iz damolst geven

243
00:12:28,381 --> 00:12:30,825
nit keyn fule draytsn yor. dos iz umgefer

244
00:12:30,882 --> 00:12:34,757
a yor, mer vi a yor for der krig. VOT in geto bin ikh arayn,

245
00:12:34,813 --> 00:12:36,539
a bisele elter geven

246
00:12:36,539 --> 00:12:37,524
vi itster.

247
00:12:37,581 --> 00:12:42,452
di fo-, di, di fotografye iz fargresert fun a kleyne vos iz geven gemakht

248
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:44,901
far a, far di shul.

249
00:12:44,901 --> 00:12:45,792
far a,

250
00:12:45,799 --> 00:12:50,571
 farsh- vi, di fotografye, vi oykh di vos ir hot gezen, un ⟨vider, velt⟩ zen,

251
00:12:50,571 --> 00:12:52,644
bay mir iz gornisht nit geblibn.

252
00:12:52,644 --> 00:12:55,867
dos iz alts geblibn bay bakante, bay kroyvim,

253
00:12:56,008 --> 00:12:58,267
un nokh dem hob ikh dos alts oyfgeklibn,

254
00:12:58,267 --> 00:13:00,532
un a, a teyl hot gegebn ⟨ot⟩ der,

255
00:13:00,532 --> 00:13:03,652
d- onkl vos iz geven in Erets-Yisroel. bay im iz dos geven geblibn.

256
00:13:03,652 --> 00:13:05,395
dos iz shoyn iberfotografirt

257
00:13:05,395 --> 00:13:08,372
un a bisele retushirt. deriber zet dos oys azoy,

258
00:13:08,378 --> 00:13:10,737
 efsher a bisele tsu, tsu groys.

259
00:13:10,737 --> 00:13:13,022
nor ot di fotografye, muz ikh aykh zogn,

260
00:13:13,022 --> 00:13:15,327
hobn oysgenutst kimat ale

261
00:13:15,327 --> 00:13:18,137
farlagn vos hobn aroysgegebn dem bikhl.

262
00:13:18,137 --> 00:13:19,858
in Helsinki,

263
00:13:19,858 --> 00:13:22,929
in, Daytshland, in di gevezene G.D.R.,

264
00:13:22,929 --> 00:13:27,035
in, Estraykhn. umetum. in Frankraykh.

265
00:13:27,447 --> 00:13:29,072
umetum hobn zey gegebn,

266
00:13:29,072 --> 00:13:31,312
 di fotografye, az me zol zen

267
00:13:31,312 --> 00:13:34,114
ver es iz der mekhaber fun, fun bukh.

268
00:13:33,533 --> 00:13:36,766
fun bukh. ven iz, ve- fun ven iz dos fotografye?

269
00:13:36,407 --> 00:13:39,391
di fotografye iz, umgefer, fun

270
00:13:39,391 --> 00:13:41,188
toyznt nayn hundert,

271
00:13:41,188 --> 00:13:44,721
 f- nay- ende nayn un draysik, onheyb fertsik.

272
00:13:44,044 --> 00:13:45,044
.

273
00:13:45,044 --> 00:13:48,022
AND, vu, vu ⟨hostu⟩ genumen di fotograf?

274
00:13:47,629 --> 00:13:52,671
di fotografye iz geblibn bay dem onkl vos iz geven in, in Erets-Yisroel.

275
00:13:52,431 --> 00:13:53,178
aha.

276
00:13:52,671 --> 00:13:57,073
er hot ge- tsugeshikt a kleyninke, dos vos iz bay im geblibn, vos ikh hob im a mol im geshikt

277
00:13:57,130 --> 00:13:58,102
a briv.

278
00:13:57,906 --> 00:13:58,932
a dank.

279
00:13:58,159 --> 00:14:00,189
ale fotografyes zaynen fun,

280
00:14:00,189 --> 00:14:02,945
⟨f-⟩ tsunoyfgeklibn fun mentshn; bay mir iz keyn zakh nito.

281
00:14:02,617 --> 00:14:04,768
OKAY. DID YOU CHECK THE BATTERY?

282
00:14:05,986 --> 00:14:06,816
OKAY.

283
00:14:07,896 --> 00:14:12,632
nu, dos iz di mame. ir hot ir shoyn gezen oyf di fotografye vos ⟨i-⟩ di gantse mishpokhe.

284
00:14:13,228 --> 00:14:15,011
do iz zi a bisele yinger.

285
00:14:15,456 --> 00:14:19,317
dos, di genoye date veys ikh nit. dos iz nor geven

286
00:14:19,317 --> 00:14:21,966
az ikh bin geven in gantsn a, a kleyninke.

287
00:14:21,835 --> 00:14:22,666
⟨he⟩.

288
00:14:23,083 --> 00:14:24,514
in geto iz zi shoyn

289
00:14:24,514 --> 00:14:26,857
geven nit enlekh tsu zikh, tsum badoyern.

290
00:14:27,285 --> 00:14:29,771
nu, vos ken a tokhter zogn vegn a mamen?

291
00:14:29,771 --> 00:14:32,462
ale mames zaynen gute, un a yidishe mame...

292
00:14:32,462 --> 00:14:34,102
dos iz a yidishe mame.

293
00:14:37,697 --> 00:14:39,800
dos iz di fotografye, ⟨ir⟩ farshteyt,

294
00:14:40,330 --> 00:14:42,079
eybik oyf mayn shrayb-tish.

295
00:14:42,287 --> 00:14:43,732
 ikh arbet un ikh kuk

296
00:14:44,346 --> 00:14:45,588
zey in di oygn.

297
00:14:46,978 --> 00:14:49,959
dos iz Rayele, shteyt, un Ruvele zitst.

298
00:14:51,585 --> 00:14:53,176
⟨s'iz⟩ umgefer tsvey yor

299
00:14:53,176 --> 00:14:56,591
forn krig. ven es hot zikh ongehoybn di krig, zey zaynen arayn in geto,

300
00:14:56,985 --> 00:15:00,289
iz Rayelen geven zibn yor, Ruvelen finf yor.

301
00:15:00,289 --> 00:15:01,890
do iz ir umgefer

302
00:15:01,963 --> 00:15:02,868
finf.

303
00:15:03,668 --> 00:15:06,109
er iz ⟨af-⟩ ⟨dokh⟩ in gantsn a kleyninker.

304
00:15:08,005 --> 00:15:08,977
a mol,

305
00:15:09,675 --> 00:15:12,723
ven es iz aroys der bikhl, nokh mit etlekhe tsendlik yor tsurik,

306
00:15:13,017 --> 00:15:14,428
hot di Leningrader

307
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:17,330
televizye genumen bay mir a intervyu,

308
00:15:18,822 --> 00:15:21,735
un der rezhisor hot mistame moyre gehat

309
00:15:22,146 --> 00:15:23,979
az in mayn shtim vet zayn

310
00:15:26,112 --> 00:15:27,754
oder tsu veynik veytog,

311
00:15:27,754 --> 00:15:30,240
oder tsu veynik protest kegn fashizm.

312
00:15:30,617 --> 00:15:34,948
hot er mir avekgeshtelt di tsvey fotografyes, az ikh zol kukn oyf zey un reydn.

313
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:38,171
ikh darf nit kukn oyf zey;

314
00:15:39,882 --> 00:15:41,935
der veytog iz azoy oykh groys,

315
00:15:43,088 --> 00:15:43,942
nor,

316
00:15:44,404 --> 00:15:45,663
⟨⟩, for mir,

317
00:15:46,767 --> 00:15:47,987
in mayn tsimer,

318
00:15:47,987 --> 00:15:49,174
vu ikh arbet,

319
00:15:49,467 --> 00:15:52,886
oyfn televizor shteyt di tsvey fotografyes fun papen un mamen,

320
00:15:53,196 --> 00:15:54,793
un oyfn shrayb-tish

321
00:15:55,980 --> 00:15:58,415
shteyt di fotografye fun beyde kinder,

322
00:15:58,415 --> 00:16:00,125
un mir dakht zikh az shtendik

323
00:16:00,773 --> 00:16:02,674
kukn zey oyf mir un fregn,

324
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,462
tsi ikh leb azoy,

325
00:16:06,156 --> 00:16:09,170
tsi ikh tu alts az mer zoln azelkhe kinder, zol men nit

326
00:16:09,345 --> 00:16:10,317
dershisn.

327
00:16:17,158 --> 00:16:19,126
 dos iz der lager STUTTHOF,

328
00:16:19,302 --> 00:16:21,743
vu ikh bin geven, vegn velkhn kh'hob, ⟨⟩, dertseylt,

329
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:25,100
ober di foto iz a itstike, shoyn nokh der milkhome.

330
00:16:25,242 --> 00:16:27,430
vi ir zet, zaynen arum un arum,

331
00:16:27,807 --> 00:16:29,438
 boymer oysgevaksn,

332
00:16:29,612 --> 00:16:31,462
dos vos damolst iz nit geven.

333
00:16:32,532 --> 00:16:36,542
 eyn kleyne, bamerkung: ot do zet zikh a vegele.

334
00:16:36,902 --> 00:16:37,874
mir

335
00:16:38,202 --> 00:16:42,581
hobn nit getort geyn durkh di vegele. dos iz geven nor far di S.S. layte.

336
00:16:42,581 --> 00:16:44,602
mir hobn gemuzt aribershprayzn,

337
00:16:44,602 --> 00:16:47,341
es zol keyn zamdele nit aroyffaln oyf der veg.

338
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:52,466
un do zet zikh a teyl fun barakn, velkhe zaynen geblibn. der lager iz nit a gantser geblibn.

339
00:16:52,466 --> 00:16:53,939
do iz itster a muzey.

340
00:16:53,997 --> 00:16:55,624
"⟨LAGER STUTTHOFS⟩".

341
00:16:58,755 --> 00:16:59,899
dos bin ikh,

342
00:16:59,899 --> 00:17:03,828
umgefer in nayntsn zeks un fertsik, dos heyst in a yor arum,

343
00:17:04,122 --> 00:17:06,276
 nokh di, nokhn bafrayung.

344
00:17:06,433 --> 00:17:10,966
dos iz oykh fargresert fun a kleyne foto vos ikh hob gehat gedarft makhn oyfn pas.

345
00:17:11,157 --> 00:17:16,078
vi ir zet, es zaynen shoyn do opgevaksn di hor, vayle in lager zaynen mir geven in gantsn one hor.

346
00:17:16,288 --> 00:17:21,331
nu, un shoyn a bisele enlekh oyf a mentshn, vayl nokhn bafrayung hob ikh gevag- hob ikh gevegt

347
00:17:21,331 --> 00:17:22,678
akht un draysik kilo.

348
00:17:24,135 --> 00:17:27,318
⟨⟩, di fotografye iz oykh in a sakh bikher oysgenutst.

349
00:17:29,147 --> 00:17:30,845
mer vi veytog in di oygn

350
00:17:31,071 --> 00:17:32,314
ze ikh do nit.

351
00:17:33,259 --> 00:17:34,594
sheynem dank aykh.

352
00:17:34,444 --> 00:17:35,444
⟨DA⟩.

353
00:17:35,057 --> 00:17:36,381
'KAY, WE'RE DONE.

